OL,3,CJersey Lifeboat Association suspension
OL,4,C'unjust and oppressive'
OL,6,FThe suspension of the Jersey Lifeboat
OL,7,FAssociation (JLA) as a search and
OL,8,Frescue asset back in December 2021 was
OL,9,F"excessive, unjust, and oppressive",
OL,10,Faccording to the island's Complaints
OL,11,FBoard.
OL,13,FThe group was stopped from operating
OL,14,Fby the Harbour and Airport Authorities
OL,15,FCommittee following a report into an
OL,16,Fincident that saw one of its lifeboats
OL,17,Fhit rocks near Noirmont.
