OL,3,CJersey Lifeboat Association suspension
OL,4,C'unjust and oppressive'
OL,6,FThe Board says it is "surprising" that
OL,7,Fwithin a day of receiving the
OL,8,Fpreliminary draft outcome of the
OL,9,Finvestigation, the Harbourmaster
OL,10,Frecommended a temporary suspension of
OL,11,Fthe JLA's status.
OL,13,FThe Harbour and Airport Authorities
OL,14,FCommittee accepted this suggestion,
OL,15,Fciting a supposed recommendation from
OL,16,Fthe independent report that there
OL,17,Fshould be an immediate review and
OL,18,Faudit of the JLA - however, no such
OL,19,Frecommendation has been found.
