OL,3,CJersey Lifeboat Association suspension
OL,4,C'unjust and oppressive'
OL,6,FThe Board considers this statement by
OL,7,Fthe Committee to be "deliberately
OL,8,Fmisleading".
OL,10,FIt also criticises how the report was
OL,11,Fproduced and published as the
OL,12,FHarbourmaster was sent an advanced
OL,13,Fcopy, although the Board is satisfied
OL,14,Fthat all conclusions were reached
OL,15,Findependently by author Marico Marine.
OL,17,FFormer chairman of the JLA, Ben
OL,18,FShenton, resigned from his position as
OL,19,Fa direct result of the events and
OL,20,Fbrought this complaint.
